<div type="edition" xml:lang="san-Latn" rendition="class:83225 maturity:83211"><!--
Comments below by Csaba Kiss are offered "as is" and do not represent a thoroughly researched or considered opinion.
--><p><lb
n="1"/>svasti kailāsa-kūṭa-bhavanād bhagavat-paśupati-<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->bhaṭṭāraka-pādā</supplied><!--
L1. B. omits <supplied reason="undefined">bhaṭṭārakapāda</supplied> (sic)
--><lb
n="2" break="no"/>nugr̥<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->hīto</supplied> bappa-pādānudhyātaḥ śrī-<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->mahā-sāmantāṁśuvarmā</supplied>
<lb
n="3"/>kuśalī vartamāna-bhaviṣyato mā <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->ku</supplied><!--
L2. B. omits <supplied reason="undefined">kuśalī</supplied>
--><!--
L2. B. omits mā. Probably to be restored as mā<supplied reason="undefined">ṭiṅ-grāma-kuṭumbino yathārhaṁ</supplied>
--><lb
n="4" break="no"/>śalam ābhāṣya samājñāpayati viditam bhavatu bhavatāṁ <supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->yathāsmābhi</supplied><!--
L4. B. omils <supplied reason="undefined">ku</supplied>śalam ābhāṣya
--><!--
L4. yathāsmābhi: Certain integration. It is omitted by B.
--><lb
n="5" break="no"/>r māṭin-deva-kulam ardha-vinipatiteṣṭakāpaṅkti-vivara-praviṣṭa<!--
L5. beginning of line: B. reads - - nr̥pakulam atha°
--><lb
n="6" break="no"/>-nakula-kulākulita-mūṣikā-sārtha-dūra-vighaṭita-nirava<!--
L6. B. has °mūṣika - - pura vighaṭita nirava
--><lb
n="7" break="no"/>śeṣa-dvāraka-vāṭa-vātāyanādi-jīrṇa-dāru-saṅghātaṁ yatnataḥ
<lb
n="8"/>pratisaṁskārya tasya dī<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->rgha</supplied>tara-paścāt-kāla-sausthitya-nimittaṁ
<lb
n="9"/>tad-akṣaya-nīvi-pratibaddham evaṁ māṭiṅ-grāmasya dakṣiṇato rāja<!--
L9. B.: °nimiṭṭa (9) <supplied reason="undefined">ma</supplied>kṣaya
--><lb
n="10"/>bhogyatām āpannaṁ viṁśatikayā catuḥ-ṣaṣṭi-mānikā-piṇḍakāṁ kṣe<lb
n="11" break="no"/>tram dakṣiṇa-paścimataś ca ṣaṇ-mānikā-piṇḍakam māṭiṅ-grāma-pā<!--
L11. B. has viṁśatikaya - - ṣaṣṭimānikapiṇḍakāṁ kṣe (11) tram. °piṇḍakāṁ is a probable mistake for °piṇḍakaṁ
--><lb
n="12" break="no"/>ñcālikebhyaḥ pratipāditam evaṁ-vedibhir na kaiścid asmat-pāda-
<lb
n="13"/>pratibaddha-jīvanair anyair vāyan dharmādhikāro <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>nyathā karaṇīyo<!--
L13. B.: karaṇīya<supplied reason="undefined">ḥ</supplied>
--><lb
n="14"/>yas tv etām ājñām ullaṅghyānyathā kuryāt kārayed vā taṁ vayan na ma<lb
n="15" break="no"/>rṣayiṣyāmo bhaviṣyadbhir api bhūpatibhir dharma-gurubhir dharmādhi<!--
L15.  B.: mā<supplied reason="undefined">rṣa</supplied>yayiṣyāmo; B.: bhavaṣyidbhir
--><lb
n="16" break="no"/>kāra-pratipālanādr̥tair bhavitavyam saṁvaT <num value="34"><g type="numeral">30</g> 4</num> prathama-pauṣa-
<lb
n="17"/>śukla-dvitīyāyām dūtako <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>tra mahā-balādhyakṣa-vindusvāmī||
</p>
